  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine in community-derived patients with gout the
      effectiveness, and cost effectiveness, of a nurse-led complex intervention that reflects
      recommended best practice (including patient information concerning gout, its prognosis and
      its non-pharmacological and drug options).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
